window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nick Summerland recently became a Medium, and he's definitely in over his head.</p> <p>Just as he was getting used to studying magic, exploring the dynamics of dating his Shade girlfriend, and drawing closer to the knowledge meant to save his best friend’s life, Nick’s assigned a special case by the Dean.</p> <p>In order to help the fiery, alluring Specter, Nick must push his magic to the limits and crack a mystery only he can solve.</p> <p>Nick’s battled horrors from Limbo, but now he’s facing off against deadly forces that are hiding the truth. And they'll do anything to stop him.</p>"; 
